<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="en"> <head> <meta charset="UTF-8"> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <title>3d Party Blueprint</title> <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script> <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"> <script> tailwind.config = { theme: { extend: { colors: { party: { dark: '#0f0f1a', card: '#1a1a2e', accent: '#FFD700' } } } } } </script> </head> <body class="bg-party-dark text-white min-h-screen"> <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20"> <a href="/" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-party-accent mb-8 inline-flex items-center space-x-2"> <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i><span>Back</span> </a> <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">3d Party Blueprint</h1> <div class="prose prose-invert"> <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">Our vision is to create a truly independent political movement in Maldives that operates outside traditional party systems.</p> <p class="text-gray-400">The 3d Party is built on three core principles:</p> <ol class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400"> <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> No insider connections or backroom deals. All contributions and activities are publicly visible.</li> <li><strong>Merit-based Influence:</strong> Your impact is determined by your actual contributions - skills, effort, donations, and physical work - not by your connections.</li> <li><strong>Grassroots Action:</strong> Real change comes from people working together on the ground, not from theoretical debates.</li> </ol> <p class="text-gray-400 mt-6">We're not an insurance company, we're a political movement that actually does things. Join us in building a better Maldives.</p> </div> </div> </body> </html> </parameter> <parameter=task_progress> - [ ] Create blueprint.html file to fix missing connection from index.html - [ ] Add back link to home page in admin.html - [ ] Verify all pages are now connected </parameter> </write_to_file>